msgstr ""
"Den mindste micro-via-hulstørrelse. Hvis angivet, kan denne kun reduceres af "
"brugerdefinerede regler."

#: pcbnew/dialogs/panel_setup_constraints_base.cpp:300
msgid "Silk"
msgstr "Silke"

#: pcbnew/dialogs/panel_setup_constraints_base.cpp:328
msgid "Minimum item clearance:"
msgstr "Minimumsafstand:"

#: pcbnew/dialogs/panel_setup_constraints_base.cpp:333
msgid ""
"Minimum clearance between two items on the same silkscreen layer. If set "
"this can improve legibility.  (Note: does not apply to multiple shapes "
"within a single footprint.)"
msgstr ""
"Minimal afstand mellem to elementer på samme silketryksag. Hvis sat kan det "
"forbedre læsbarheden. (Bemærk: gælder ikke for flere former inden for et "
"enkelt fodaftryk.)"

#: pcbnew/dialogs/panel_setup_constraints_base.cpp:344
msgid "Minimum text height:"
msgstr "Minimum teksthøjde:"

#: pcbnew/dialogs/panel_setup_constraints_base.cpp:358
msgid "Minimum text thickness:"
msgstr "Minimum teksttykkelse:"

#: pcbnew/dialogs/panel_setup_constraints_base.cpp:384
msgid "Arc/Circle Approximations"
msgstr "Bue-/cirkelapproksimationer"

#: pcbnew/dialogs/panel_setup_constraints_base.cpp:397
msgid "Maximum allowed deviation:"
msgstr "Maksimal tilladt afvigelse:"

#: pcbnew/dialogs/panel_setup_constraints_base.cpp:399
msgid ""
"This is the maximum distance between a circle and the polygonal shape that "
"approximate it.\n"
"The error max defines the number of segments of this polygon."
msgstr ""
"Dette er den maksimale afstand mellem en cirkel og den polygonale form, der "
"tilnærmer sig den.\n"
"Fejlen max definerer antallet af segmenter af denne polygon."

